# Frontend app conventions

## Layout

- `app/<route>/page.tsx` — server component, thin wrapper
- `features/<domain>/<name>-page.tsx` — `"use client"` feature UI
- `components/` — shells and layout only (`AdminShell`, `WorkspaceShell`)

## Shared code

Use `@kloqra/web-shared` for API client, downloads, session/workspace stores, providers, date helpers.

Use `@kloqra/ui` for design primitives (`Button`, `Card`, `PageHeader`, etc.).

## Rules

- `"use client"` only where hooks, browser APIs, or interactivity are required
- Authenticated calls: `api()` from web-shared; public token pages: `publicFetch()`
- State: Zustand stores in web-shared or app-specific `stores/`
- Types: `@kloqra/contracts` only — no duplicate DTO shapes
